OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FVariable cloud with some long
OL,6,Fsunny periods during the day, clouding
OL,7,Fover during the evening with the
OL,8,Fchance of some showers by the morning.
OL,9,FWinds light and variable.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,12,FTurning more unsettled on Tuesday with
OL,13,Fsunshine and showers. Wednesday starts
OL,14,Fof sunny, then clouding over with
OL,15,Fshowers later. A dry start on Thursday
OL,16,Fbefore clouding over with heavy
OL,17,Fshowers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
